<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Breaking Bad Fan Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #111;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #66cc33;
        }
        nav {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #66cc33;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .character, .episode {
            border: 1px solid #666;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 200px;
        }
        .character img, .episode img {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .character h2, .episode h2 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #666;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
        section {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Breaking Bad Fan Page</h1>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#characters">Characters</a>
        <a href="#episodes">Episodes</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="content">
        <section id="home">
            <h2>Welcome to the Breaking Bad Fan Page</h2>
            <p>Discover the world of Breaking Bad, the hit TV series that captivated audiences worldwide.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="characters">
            <h2>Characters</h2>
            <div class="character">
                <img src="https://2024.imaginaryctf.org/img/pfp/firepony.gif" alt="Walter White">
                <h2>Walter White</h2>
                <p>The main character, a chemistry teacher turned methamphetamine manufacturer.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
                <img src="https://2024.imaginaryctf.org/img/pfp/et3rnos.png" alt="Jesse Pinkman">
                <h2>Jesse Pinkman</h2>
                <p>Walter's former student and business partner in the methamphetamine trade.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
                <img src="https://2024.imaginaryctf.org/img/pfp/eth007.png" alt="Skyler White">
                <h2>Skyler White</h2>
                <p>Walter's wife, who becomes increasingly involved in his illegal activities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
                <img src="https://2024.imaginaryctf.org/img/pfp/astro.png" alt="Hank Schrader">
                <h2>Hank Schrader</h2>
                <p>Walter's brother-in-law, a DEA agent determined to catch Heisenberg.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="episodes">
            <h2>Episodes</h2>
            <div class="episode">
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS2AetEB-NLXibxtwZuoUAQfMqJ-40JgX2pYw&s" alt="Pilot">
                <h2>Pilot</h2>
                <p>The first episode where we meet Walter White and learn about his cancer diagnosis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="episode">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fc/Genetta_genetta_felina.JPG" alt="Felina">
                <h2>Felina</h2>
                <p>The final episode where Walter's journey comes to a dramatic conclusion.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="episode">
                <img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/2433/3597919375_a32b005961_b.jpg" alt="Ozymandias">
                <h2>Ozymandias</h2>
                <p>Widely regarded as the best episode, where Walter's empire begins to crumble.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>This fan page is dedicated to the critically acclaimed TV series Breaking Bad. Here, you can find information about the characters, episodes, and more.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
